---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';

// 1. Import the Image component for optimization
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';

// 2. Import your specific logos from src/assets/logos/
import MastercardLogo from '../assets/mcf.webp';
import EduCollabLogo from '../assets/educollab.png';
import AshesiEntrepLogo from '../assets/ashesi_entrepreneurship_center_logo.jpeg';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
		<style>
			main { width: calc(100% - 2em); max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3em 1em; }
			h1 { color: #111827; font-size: 3.5rem; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 0.5em; font-weight: 800; }
			.hero-text { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
			
			section { margin-bottom: 5rem; }
			
			h2 { border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #1f2937; font-size: 2rem; }
			
			.highlight-box { background: #f9fafb; border-left: 4px solid #1e3a8a; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; font-style: italic; color: #374151; }
			
			ul { list-style-type: none; padding: 0; }
			li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; color: #4b5563; }
			li::before { content: "→"; position: absolute; left: 0; color: #1e3a8a; font-weight: bold; }

			/* References Section Styling */
			.references-container {
				background-color: #1a365d; /* Dark Navy Blue */
				padding: 4rem 2rem;
				margin: 4rem -2em; /* Bleeds out to edges */
				text-align: center;
				border-radius: 12px;
			}

			.references-container h2 {
				color: white;
				font-family: serif; 
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				border: none;
				text-align: center;
			}

			.reference-grid {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
				gap: 1.5rem;
				max-width: 1000px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}

			.ref-card {
				background: white;
				height: 140px;
				display: flex;
				align-items: center;
				justify-content: center;
				border-radius: 20px;
				padding: 1.5rem;
				box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
				transition: transform 0.2s ease;
			}

			.ref-card:hover {
				transform: translateY(-5px);
			}

			.ref-card img {
				max-width: 90%;
				max-height: 80%;
				width: auto;
				height: auto;
				object-fit: contain;
			}

			@media (max-width: 720px) {
				h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; }
				.references-container { margin: 4rem 0; }
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<section>
				<h1>Access Without Fear.</h1>
				<p class="hero-text">
					<strong>Pouls</strong> is a student-led health equity initiative dismantling medical stigma 
					in Zimbabwe. We are bridging the gap between campus dorms and professional care through 
					anonymity, technology, and empathy.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>The UZ Tragedy: Why We Build</h2>
				<p>
					In 2024, a student at the University of Zimbabwe lost their life to a preventable condition. 
					They didn't die from a lack of medicine, but because the <strong>social cost of 
					seeking help</strong>—fear of judgment and administrative exposure—was too high.
				</p>
				<div class="highlight-box">
					"We are building a digital sanctuary where 'access' is defined by privacy, not bureaucracy."
				</div>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Technical Infrastructure</h2>
				<p>Our dual-dashboard system leverages secure software architecture to protect student identities:</p>
				<ul>
					<li><strong>Anonymous Student Portal:</strong> Encrypted triage system that prioritizes user safety and data stripping.</li>
					<li><strong>Practitioner Interface:</strong> A specialized diagnostic hub for verified responders to manage care without bias.</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section class="references-container">
				<h2>References</h2>
				<div class="reference-grid">
					<div class="ref-card">
						<Image src={MastercardLogo} alt="Mastercard Foundation Logo" />
					</div>

					<div class="ref-card">
						<Image src={EduCollabLogo} alt="Ashesi Education Collaborative Logo" />
					</div>

					<div class="ref-card">
						<Image src={AshesiEntrepLogo} alt="Ashesi Entrepreneurship Center Logo" />
					</div>
				</div>
			</section>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>